    Y\xEAu c\u1EA7u: C\xF3 s\u1EA3n ph\u1EA9m game t\u1EF1 l\xE0m, hi\u1EC3u r\xF5
    C# v\xE0 c\u1EA5u tr\xFAc d\u1EEF li\u1EC7u.<br>\u2022 L\u01B0\u01A1ng h\u1ED7
    tr\u1EE3: 1.000.000\u0111/th\xE1ng. Th\u1EED vi\u1EC7c kh\xF4ng l\u01B0\u01A1ng
    2 th\xE1ng.<br><br><color=#8ab4f8><size=13><b>2. L\u1EADp Tr\xECnh Vi\xEAn Web
    (Fresher) - VinaTech Group</b></size></color><br><color=#9aa0a6><size=10>https://vinatech.com/careers/web-fresher</size></color><br>\u2022
    Y\xEAu c\u1EA7u: C\xF3 t\u1ED1i thi\u1EC3u 1 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1EC7m l\xE0m
    vi\u1EC7c th\u1EF1c t\u1EBF t\u1EA1i doanh nghi\u1EC7p.<br>\u2022 M\u1EE9c l\u01B0\u01A1ng:
    6.000.000\u0111 - 8.000.000\u0111. Ph\u1ECFng v\u1EA5n k\u1EF9 thu\u1EADt 3 v\xF2ng.<br><br><color=#33cc66><size=13><b>3.
    [HOT] Vi\u1EC7c L\xE0m N\u01B0\u1EDBc Ngo\xE0i L\u01B0\u01A1ng Cao - Tuy\u1EC3n
    K\u1EF9 Thu\u1EADt Vi\xEAn M\xE1y T\xEDnh (Campuchia)</b></size></color><br><color=#9aa0a6><size=10>https://vieclamnuocngoai.com/tuyen-dung/cambodia-tech</size></color><br>\u2022
    M\u1EE9c l\u01B0\u01A1ng: 1.000.000\u0111 - 1.500.000\u0111/ng\xE0y (Bao \u0103n
    \u1EDF to\xE0n b\u1ED9, h\u1ED7 tr\u1EE3 xe \u0111\u01B0a \u0111\xF3n, kh\xF4ng
    ph\xED trung gian).<br>\u2022 Y\xEAu c\u1EA7u: Bi\u1EBFt s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng m\xE1y
    t\xEDnh c\u01A1 b\u1EA3n, g\xF5 ph\xEDm nhanh. Kh\xF4ng y\xEAu c\u1EA7u b\u1EB1ng
    c\u1EA5p hay kinh nghi\u1EC7m.<br><br><color=#ffcc00><i>C\u1EA3nh b\xE1o th\u1ECB
    tr\u01B0\u1EDDng:</i></color> <i>Th\u1ECB tr\u01B0\u1EDDng tuy\u1EC3n d\u1EE5ng
    IT n\u0103m 2026 \u0111ang c\xF3 m\u1EE9c \u0111\u1ED9 c\u1EA1nh tranh r\u1EA5t
    cao. C\u1EA3nh gi\xE1c v\u1EDBi c\xE1c tin tuy\u1EC3n d\u1EE5ng vi\u1EC7c nh\u1EB9
    l\u01B0\u01A1ng cao \u1EDF n\u01B0\u1EDBc ngo\xE0i, n\u1EA1p ti\u1EC1n c\u1ECDc
    l\xE0m nhi\u1EC7m v\u1EE5.</i>"
